The '''Ghilron pirates''' was a band of [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]], which operated in the area around the [[Sisar Run/Legends|Sisar Run]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. They were enemies of the [[Disac pirates]].

